Post-August is the best time of the year, especially for the millennials with lots of festivals coming up. 
They save their leaves so that they can travel without anything bothering them. 
Slow and meaningful travel has already picked up India and travellers have realised the essence of the same. 
Karnataka is blessed to have many tourist attractions that one can plan over a weekend. 
Bangalore being the most well-connected destination is the base for all travels not only in Karnataka but the whole of South India. 
Long weekend getaways from Bangalore are something everyone is always looking for.
There are several destinations within a 300 km range from Bangalore that can be considered for long weekend getaways.
